 ## Snake Game – Phasing Plan
 
-I am a cat
+Phase 1 – Skeleton
+Drop a canvas on the page, wire up a game loop, paint a black background. Prove the motor runs.
+
+Phase 2 – Snake
+Draw a moving white line. Accept arrow keys to steer. Keep the snake on screen.
+
+Phase 3 – Food
+Spawn red square at random grid spot. Detect collision, grow snake, respawn food.
+
+Phase 4 – Game Over
+End game on wall or self collision. Show score, offer restart.